videos.description: Dominic Green creates space with a pump fake and knocks down a three for Providence.
videos.headline: Providence's Green uses pump fake to knock down three

videos.description: Matisse Thybulle rises up for the alley-oop on the fast break for Washington.
videos.headline: Washington's Thybulle throws it down after a steal

videos.description: Kalif Young finishes with defenders draped all over him for Providence.
videos.headline: Providence's Young finishes over three defenders

videos.description: Rodney Bullock knocks down a three to extend the lead for Providence.
videos.headline: Providence's Bullock grabs rebound, trails, knocks down three

videos.description: Kalif Young gets the shot to go after a tough foul.
videos.headline: UW's Young gets tough and-1 to go
